text: The Final Frontier is an album by Iron Maiden. It was announced on 4 March 2010, along a concert tour. It was recorded in The Bahamas and produced by Kevin Shirley. The album began being sold on 17 August 2010. It sold very well, being the most popular album in 21 countries when it went on sale, as well as being one of the top five most popular albums in eight other countries. ==Musicians== * Bruce Dickinson - vocals * Janick Gers - guitar * Steve Harris - bass guitar * Nicko McBrain - percussion * Dave Murray - guitar * Adrian Smith - guitar ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2010 albums Category:Iron Maiden albums
title: The Final Frontier
